item.title: 【HD Live Performances】WEB-RiP - Mike Shinoda - Already Over Sessions
item.description:
Mike Shinoda - Already Over Sessions
Mike's going around the world and performing his latest song Already Over with another random song with local talented artists who he find them on social media.
4 episodes released so far. If he share more episodes I will update this post
